==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Huyghenian
<hw>Huy*ghe"ni*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to,
or invented by, Christian <xex>Huyghens</xex>, a Dutch astronomer of the
seventeenth century; <as>as, the <ex>Huyghenian</ex>
telescope</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Huyghenian eyepiece</b></col><cd>See under
<er>Eyepiece</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Huzz</ent>⟦br⟧
